    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "**Build Speaker Split Lists**\n",
        "\n",
        "Create speaker level sets for the train, validation, and test partitions using the datasplit field in the metadata. These sets ensure that recordings from the same speaker remain within a single dataset split."
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "XJyqjxTpf8KY"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "train_speakers = set(metadata[metadata[\"datasplit\"] == \"train\"][\"speaker\"])\n",
        "valid_speakers = set(metadata[metadata[\"datasplit\"] == \"valid\"][\"speaker\"])\n",
        "test_speakers = set(metadata[metadata[\"datasplit\"] == \"test\"][\"speaker\"])\n",
        "\n",
        "print(\"train speakers:\", len(train_speakers))\n",
        "print(\"valid speakers:\", len(valid_speakers))\n",
        "print(\"test speakers:\", len(test_speakers))"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/"
        },
        "id": "QLUV0Nmqf8AC",
        "outputId": "8d189b8e-94c7-4525-dced-817e8e18b396"
      },
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": [
        {
          "output_type": "stream",
